{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idcf647023-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0","identifier":"/us/usc/t48/s915"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"915"},"text":"§ 915.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Bonds as public debt","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Such bonds shall not be a debt of Puerto Rico or any municipality, and shall not constitute a public indebtedness within the meaning of section 3 of the Act of Congress approved ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1917-03-02"},"text":"March 2, 1917","children":[],"tail":", entitled “An Act to provide a civil government for Porto Rico, and for other purposes”, as amended."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idcf647024-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1938-06-25/ch703/s5"},"text":"June 25, 1938, ch. 703, § 5","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/52/1203"},"text":"52 Stat. 1203","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idcf647025-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idcf647026-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idcf647027-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 3 of the Act of Congress approved ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1917-03-02"},"text":"March 2, 1917","children":[],"tail":", referred to in text, is section 3 of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1917-03-02/ch145"},"text":"act Mar. 2, 1917, ch. 145","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/39/953"},"text":"39 Stat. 953","children":[],"tail":". The provisions of section 3 of the Act limiting the public indebtedness of Puerto Rico and of certain municipalities thereof were contained in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t48/s745"},"text":"section 745 of this title","children":[],"tail":", prior to the amendment made to that section by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/121/s1"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–121, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1961-08-03"},"text":"Aug. 3, 1961","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/75/245"},"text":"75 Stat. 245","children":[],"tail":", which struck out those provisions. See 1961 Amendment note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t48/s745"},"text":"section 745 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idcf647028-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was not enacted as part of the Puerto Rican Federal Relations Act which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
